ActPublic Sector Pension Investment Board Act
PrecisAppointment of WILLIAM A. MacKINNON of Toronto, Ontario, to be a director of the Public Sector Pension Investment Board to hold office during good behaviour for a term of four years, in the place of Keith G. Martell.
